channel.title: AncientBlitz - 90% Hunter | Custom Construction | Awesome Features
channel.description:
[center]This is my new project, ALL CREDITS GO TO ASSHOLE_RULE AND IMSUPERMAN05 for now! This is based off their release, super_asshole or something like that. The only thing I have done is fixed the client because it did not work, but like I said all credits go to them for now. I'm in need of a client developer because they are many client sided issues, I do both client and server sided but I've only started working on client's in January I know alot about them but this is just something I've never seen. Scroll bars do not work, Prayer tab freezes client and some issues with random things freezing the client, sometimes dieing will freeze not all the time and other random things, none of these show an exact error of why or where you can fix it so I will need someone that will know this. I'm not listing this for someone to post down there and help me, I'm posting so if your applying you know what your going to be working for. I have one other server developer OmgItsShane and I'm a server developer + Client, IF i get a client developer I will most likely be working just on server but I will help if they need any help with any little things. Now for the media and application format.
Media! Bird hunter! [img]http://img685.imageshack.us/img685/6821/birdai.png[/img] Hunting Chinchompas! [img]http://img215.imageshack.us/img215/9580/chins.png[/img] New Maps! [img]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/3389/coolplace.png[/img] [img]http://img109.imageshack.us/img109/9007/coolplace2.png[/img] Grand Exchange! [img]http://img267.imageshack.us/img267/4240/88807980.png[/img] [img]http://img197.imageshack.us/img197/3765/ge1.png[/img] [img]http://img40.imageshack.us/img40/5584/ge2u.png[/img] [img]http://img710.imageshack.us/img710/5288/ge3.png[/img] Hunter Imp's with new awesome maps! [img]http://img18.imageshack.us/img18/3904/impso.png[/img] Summoning interfaces 100%! [img]http://img403.imageshack.us/img403/939/pocuhes.png[/img] [img]http://img593.imageshack.us/img593/8868/scrolls.png[/img] Prayer's work! [img]http://img864.imageshack.us/img864/2332/prayerj.png[/img] Construction!! [img]http://img692.imageshack.us/img692/218/80697290.png[/img]
Videos!
Construction: http://youtu.be/z2GL5BtsSK4
Application Format:
Client Programmer: [code] Name: Will you be dedicated?(Yes/No): Msn/Skype(Need one): Years of experience with clients: Years of experience with Java: What are you best at client sided("Everything" is an option): Proof of work(If your not a trusted member): [/code] [/center]
